</paragraph>
<paragraph id="394B36C8FFDDBE556F93FE770E049D2B" blockId="55.[160,1155,489,584]" box="[160,340,489,515]" pageId="55" pageNumber="499">
<emphasis id="0B80EADAFFDDBE556F93FE770E049D2B" bold="true" box="[160,340,489,515]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="499">Ecological note</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="394B36C8FFDDBE556F93FD920DF19D60" blockId="55.[160,1155,489,584]" pageId="55" pageNumber="499">
The only known specimen was collected from inside a mixed forest in a town centre near a river less than 
<quantity id="FE0C9B2DFFDDBE556E6AFDB10EC19D60" box="[345,401,559,584]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="55" pageNumber="499" unit="km" value="2.0">2 km</quantity>
